{"tid":2237849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《粉飾太平》實體展，想邀請大家","createTime":"2020-10-10T15:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T05:07:26.000Z","uid":143257,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"885f629d07ba035f891faf7f284683f4d34bff12","tid":2237849,"uid":143257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"《粉飾太平》唔知大家有印象<br />\n廢話少講，講邀請各巴絲黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wvdWRg6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvdWRg6.png&h=01007928&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXcMt4k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXcMt4k.jpg&h=83bcbd35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古市民<br />\n<br />\n最近深水埗大南街parallel space搵小弟想擺一個關於呢年幾嘅作品展，主要都係關於運動同社會。<br />\n（parallel space 係深水埗大南街一個展覽場地，我都知連登上個禮拜先插緊大南街周圍coffee shop同發展商問題，不過parallel space係兩層都純粹for 展覽嘅地方，佢哋搵我，我難得有機會擺到呢類作品，我緊係嘍飯應啦！）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然入面仲有展出小弟其他作品，都係關於運動、社會、監控、傳媒、香港同中國等方向。<br />\n<br />\n例如：用五幅世界地圖撕貼出香港地圖，其實呢個作品係當時國安法一立，我所做嘅作品。當有國家幫香港出聲，中國就話「不得干預國家內政」，但其實香港本身就係一個國際性城市，並唔係單單屬於中國⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfOcpDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfOcpDo.jpg&h=07947b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcbdTwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcbdTwM.jpg&h=a7857629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，仲有件係互動作品，係比入場觀眾自行貼上膠紙，因為係《粉飾太平》時，好多人問「貼膠紙怕唔怕犯法」，但我覺得如果連咁少事我哋都要怕，之後只會越黎越多嘢唔敢做。<br />\nDay1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdGmhZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdGmhZf.jpg&h=cd838deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay5<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5h8jO5W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5h8jO5W.jpg&h=da913a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay8<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRW12qX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRW12qX.jpg&h=192f4880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日day9<br />\n多左好多真嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55Ax85Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55Ax85Y.jpg&h=da5127a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtebFcE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtebFcE.jpg&h=17a0d323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8A6t5Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8A6t5Z.jpg&h=863b95c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好幾件其他作品，但我廢事咁長文，有興趣嘅既巴打歡迎follow 小弟ig (@gllh_art)，多多支持小弟可以繼續以藝術方式回應社會。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望各位巴絲多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n展覽日期：10月1日至10月18日（有機會延長至24-25號）<br />\n時間：每天中午 12:00 至 晚上 07:00（逢星期一休息）<br />\n地點 / Venue : Parallel Space <br />\n地址／Address :G/F, 202, Tai Nan Street, Sham Shui Po / 深水埗大南街202號<br />\n<br />\n費用：免費（場內有售明信片，希望大家支持下小弟創作同 parallel space）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟ig : gllh_art <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgllh_art%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDBx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=618fa056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/gllh_art/</a><br />\nParallel space ig: parallel_space_hk <br />\n<br />\n反思現今社會狀況係咪正常（半年前嘅post)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1898726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1898726</a>"},{"pid":"5999a23fb32f430a0bf85059e5ecd6e44024abf2","tid":2237849,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":